the way.<span>善听者，终能找到道路。</span></p>\n      <ul class=\"z05-meta\" aria-label=\"Z05 AuAg highlights\">\n        <li>Two listening moods</li><li>Hand-finished AuAg</li><li>10mm dynamic punch</li><li>3.5 / 4.4 / Type-C</li>\n      </ul>\n      <div class=\"z05-actions\"><a class=\"z05-btn\" href=\"/cart/add?id={{ product.selected_or_first_available_variant.id }}&quantity=1\">Buy Z05 AuAg</a><a class=\"z05-btn secondary\" href=\"#z05-twincore\">Hear TwinCore</a></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"z05-hero-media\">\n      <img src=\"{{ 'z05-auag-luxury-portrait-hero.png' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"Z05 AuAg Launch Edition in a minimalist gold and silver luxury studio setting\">\n    </div>\n  </section>\n  <div class=\"z05-stat-strip\"><div class=\"z05-wrap z05-stats\"><div class=\"z05-stat\"><b>TwinCore</b><span>Blue when you want weight and flow. Red when you want the mix to open up and step forward.</span></div><div class=\"z05-stat\"><b>Dynamic Bass</b><span>Kick drums and bass lines have real skin and pressure, not just a lifted low-end shelf.</span></div><div class=\"z05-stat\"><b>Hybrid Detail</b><span>Armatures bring vocal edges, cymbal air, and room cues without thinning out the body.</span></div><div class=\"z05-stat\"><b>AuAg</b><span>Forged-carbon faceplates carry the gold/silver identity; the shells are finished by hand, pair by pair.</span></div></div></div>\n</div>",
