                "custom_liquid": "<div id=\"z05-twincore\" class=\"z05-feature-shell\"><section class=\"z05-section dark z05-twincore-section\"><div class=\"z05-wrap z05-grid-2\"><div><p class=\"z05-kicker\">TwinCore</p><h2>Same monitor, two listening moods</h2><p>Some albums want warmth and weight. Others ask for cleaner edges and a little more air. TwinCore lets Z05 AuAg move between those moods with a real switch on the shell, large enough to nudge by fingernail while the monitors stay in your ears.</p><p>No tool, no tiny recessed slot, no guessing through a phone app. The action has just enough resistance, only two positions, and is easy to find by touch once you know where it sits. Think of it less like a gimmick and more like choosing the right filter, gain, or cartridge flavor before you settle into the record.</p><div class=\"z05-actions\"><a class=\"z05-btn\" href=\"/cart/add?id={{ product.selected_or_first_available_variant.id }}&quantity=1\">Buy Z05 AuAg</a></div></div><div class=\"z05-twincore-panel\"><img src=\"{{ 'z05-auag-twincore-switch-closeup.jpg' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"Z05 AuAg TwinCore switch with blue and red position markers\" loading=\"lazy\"><div class=\"z05-mode-grid\"><article><span>Blue Mode</span><h3>Weight / Flow</h3><p>A fuller low end, calmer upper harmonics, and a center image that feels easier to sit with for long albums.</p></article><article><span>Red Mode</span><h3>Focus / Spark</h3><p>Tighter bass outlines, more forward clarity, and extra cymbal air when you want the mix to open up.</p></article></div></div></div></section></div><style>.z05-twincore-section{background:#050505}.z05-twincore-section h2{max-width:760px}.z05-twincore-section p{color:#d8d1c7}.z05-twincore-panel{background:#111;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);padding:12px}.z05-twincore-panel img{display:block;width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/10;object-fit:cover}.z05-mode-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1px;margin-top:12px;background:rgba(255,255,25